# SoundByte

## SoundByte is a web application built with ASP.NET MVC and Web API for sharing audio files.. It allows users to perform CRUD (Create, Read, Update, Delete) operations on audio entries through a user-friendly interface.

### Features

    ####Audio Management:
        List all audios.
        View details of a specific audio.
        Add new audio entries.
        Edit existing audio details.
        Delete audio entries.

    ####Category Management:
        List all categories.
        View details of a specific category.
        Add new categories.
        Edit existing category details.
        Delete categories.

### Technologies Used
ASP.NET MVC, ASP.NET Web API, Entity Framework, SQL Server, HTML, CSS, Bootstrap, JavaScript, C#